    "description": "Ptolemy places this ancient city in India. BAtlas identifies it firmly with modern Kanchipuram, which is located inland and southwest from modern Chennai.",
    "details": "<p>The Barrington Atlas Directory notes: Kanchipuram. Dayalan 2019 asserts, without argument or mention of Kanchipuram, a tentative alternative identification with Mamallapuram. Nannam 2019 uncritically resurrects an early 20th century identification with Krishnapatna/Gandagopalapattana port.</p>",
